(N'PWAIT_HADR_CHANGE_NOTIFIER_TERMINATION_SYNC',N'HA_REPLICATION',2,0,N'Occurs when a background task is waiting for the termination of the background task that receives (via polling) Windows Server Failover Clustering notifications. Internal use only.',N'Availability Groups, Mirroring oder HA-Hintergrundarbeit.',N'Je Wait entweder erwarteter Idle-Zustand oder erhöhte Commit-/Redo-/Send-Latenz.',N'Benign-Flag beachten; Replica-Zustand, Queues, Netzwerk und Log-I/O prüfen.',N'REFERENCE_NORMALIZED',N'IMPORTED_REVIEW_REQUIRED'),
(N'PWAIT_HADR_CLUSTER_INTEGRATION',N'HA_REPLICATION',2,0,N'An append, replace, and/or remove operation is waiting to grab a write lock on an AlwaysOn internal list (such as a list of networks, network addresses, or availability group listeners). Internal use only.',N'Availability Groups, Mirroring oder HA-Hintergrundarbeit.',N'Je Wait entweder erwarteter Idle-Zustand oder erhöhte Commit-/Redo-/Send-Latenz.',N'Benign-Flag beachten; Replica-Zustand, Queues, Netzwerk und Log-I/O prüfen.',N'REFERENCE_NORMALIZED',N'IMPORTED_REVIEW_REQUIRED'),
(N'PWAIT_HADR_OFFLINE_COMPLETED',N'HA_REPLICATION',2,0,N'An AlwaysOn drop availability group operation is waiting for the target availability group to go offline before destroying Windows Server Failover Clustering objects.',N'Availability Groups, Mirroring oder HA-Hintergrundarbeit.',N'Je Wait entweder erwarteter Idle-Zustand oder erhöhte Commit-/Redo-/Send-Latenz.',N'Benign-Flag beachten; Replica-Zustand, Queues, Netzwerk und Log-I/O prüfen.',N'REFERENCE_NORMALIZED',N'IMPORTED_REVIEW_REQUIRED'),
(N'PWAIT_HADR_ONLINE_COMPLETED',N'HA_REPLICATION',2,0,N'An AlwaysOn create or failover availability group operation is waiting for the target availability group to come online.',N'Availability Groups, Mirroring oder HA-Hintergrundarbeit.',N'Je Wait entweder erwarteter Idle-Zustand oder erhöhte Commit-/Redo-/Send-Latenz.',N'Benign-Flag beachten; Replica-Zustand, Queues, Netzwerk und Log-I/O prüfen.',N'REFERENCE_NORMALIZED',N'IMPORTED_REVIEW_REQUIRED'),
(N'PWAIT_HADR_POST_ONLINE_COMPLETED',N'HA_REPLICATION',2,0,N'An AlwaysOn drop availability group operation is waiting for the termination of any background task that was scheduled as part of a previous command. For example, there may be a background task that is transitioning availability databases to the primary r',N'Availability Groups, Mirroring oder HA-Hintergrundarbeit.',N'Je Wait entweder erwarteter Idle-Zustand oder erhöhte Commit-/Redo-/Send-Latenz.',N'Benign-Flag beachten; Replica-Zustand, Queues, Netzwerk und Log-I/O prüfen.',N'REFERENCE_NORMALIZED',N'IMPORTED_REVIEW_REQUIRED'),
(N'PWAIT_HADR_WORKITEM_COMPLETED',N'HA_REPLICATION',2,0,N'Internal wait by a thread waiting for an async work task to complete. This is an expected wait and is for CSS use.',N'Availability Groups, Mirroring oder HA-Hintergrundarbeit.',N'Je Wait entweder erwarteter Idle-Zustand oder erhöhte Commit-/Redo-/Send-Latenz.',N'Benign-Flag beachten; Replica-Zustand, Queues, Netzwerk und Log-I/O prüfen.',N'REFERENCE_NORMALIZED',N'IMPORTED_REVIEW_REQUIRED'),
(N'QPJOB_KILL',N'STATISTICS',2,0,N'Indicates that an asynchronous automatic statistics update was canceled by a call to KILL as the update was starting to run. The terminating thread is suspended, waiting for it to start listening for KILL commands. A good value is less than one second.',N'Statistikaktualisierung oder Statistik-Hintergrundarbeit.',N'Synchrone Aktualisierung kann Kompilierung und Requeststart blockieren.',N'Statistikalter, Änderungsrate, AUTO_UPDATE_STATISTICS_ASYNC und Jobs prüfen.',N'REFERENCE_NORMALIZED',N'IMPORTED_REVIEW_REQUIRED'),
(N'QPJOB_WAITFOR_ABORT',N'STATISTICS',2,0,N'Indicates that an asynchronous automatic statistics update was canceled by a call to KILL when it was running. The update has now completed but is suspended until the terminating thread message coordination is complete. This is an ordinary but rare state,',N'Statistikaktualisierung oder Statistik-Hintergrundarbeit.',N'Synchrone Aktualisierung kann Kompilierung und Requeststart blockieren.',N'Statistikalter, Änderungsrate, AUTO_UPDATE_STATISTICS_ASYNC und Jobs prüfen.',N'REFERENCE_NORMALIZED',N'IMPORTED_REVIEW_REQUIRED'),
(N'QRY_MEM_GRANT_INFO_MUTEX',N'OTHER_OR_NEW',2,0,N'Occurs when Query Execution memory management tries to control access to static grant information list. This state lists information about the current granted and waiting memory requests. This state is a simple access control state. There should never be',N'Spezialisierter, interner oder neuer SQL-Server-Wait-Type.',N'Hohe Werte sind nur im Delta- und Workload-Kontext bewertbar.',N'Aktive Tasks, Ressource, Version, SQLskills-Detailseite und Herstellerdokumentation prüfen.',N'REFERENCE_NORMALIZED',N'IMPORTED_REVIEW_REQUIRED'),
(N'QUERY_ERRHDL_SERVICE_DONE',N'OTHER_OR_NEW',2,0,N'Identified for informational purposes only. Not supported. Future compatibility is not guaranteed.',N'Spezialisierter, interner oder neuer SQL-Server-Wait-Type.',N'Hohe Werte sind nur im Delta- und Workload-Kontext bewertbar.',N'Aktive Tasks, Ressource, Version, SQLskills-Detailseite und Herstellerdokumentation prüfen.',N'REFERENCE_NORMALIZED',N'IMPORTED_REVIEW_REQUIRED'),
(N'QUERY_EXECUTION_INDEX_SORT_EVENT_OPEN',N'OTHER_OR_NEW',2,0,N'Occurs in certain cases when offline create index build is run in parallel, and the different worker threads that are sorting synchronize access to the sort files.',N'Spezialisierter, interner oder neuer SQL-Server-Wait-Type.',N'Hohe Werte sind nur im Delta- und Workload-Kontext bewertbar.',N'Aktive Tasks, Ressource, Version, SQLskills-Detailseite und Herstellerdokumentation prüfen.',N'REFERENCE_NORMALIZED',N'IMPORTED_REVIEW_REQUIRED'),
(N'QUERY_NOTIFICATION_MGR_MUTEX',N'OTHER_OR_NEW',2,0,N'Occurs during synchronization of the garbage collection queue in the Query Notification Manager.',N'Spezialisierter, interner oder neuer SQL-Server-Wait-Type.',N'Hohe Werte sind nur im Delta- und Workload-Kontext bewertbar.',N'Aktive Tasks, Ressource, Version, SQLskills-Detailseite und Herstellerdokumentation prüfen.',N'REFERENCE_NORMALIZED',N'IMPORTED_REVIEW_REQUIRED'),
